name: Wisp (musician)
description:
'''Natalie R. Lu''' (born August 6, 2004), known professionally as '''Wisp''', is an American musician. Raised in San Francisco, she later attended [[San Francisco State University]]. 

She began releasing music in 2023. Her debut single "[[Your Face (song)|Your Face]]" became viral on [[TikTok]], charting on ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]''{{'s}} [[Hot Hard Rock Songs]]. Her debut EP, ''[[Pandora (Wisp EP)|Pandora]]'', was released in April the following year. In August 2025, she released her debut studio album, ''[[If Not Winter (album)|If Not Winter]]''.
